---
import donor2 from "../../assets/img/donor1.png";
---
<section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 flex lg:border-0 border-b-2 border-gray-300">
        <img src={donor2.src} alt="" class="lg:block hidden w-full h-full object-cover">
        <div class="bg-gray-200 py-8 lg:px-14 px-4 lg:py-16 w-full items-left justify-center flex flex-col">
            <p class="mb-1 text-lg font-bold text-red-700 lg:text-xl dark:text-red-400">RedHope Donation Steps</p>
            <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none text-gray-900 md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl dark:text-white">Donate RedHope in 4 Simple Steps</h1>   
            <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-5 lg:mt-2">
                <div class="step1 flex items-center gap-2 lg:mb-0 mb-4">
                    <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-xl bg-yellow-400 text-white lg:w-16 lg:h-14 w-12 h-12 rounded-full text-center flex items-center justify-center font-semibold">1</h1>
                    <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-xl text-left p-2 font-semibold">Eligibility Check Of Donor by Doctor</h1>
                </div>                
                <div class="step1 flex items-center gap-2 lg:mb-0 mb-4">
                    <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-xl bg-green-600 text-white lg:w-16 lg:h-14 w-12 h-12 rounded-full text-center flex items-center justify-center font-semibold">2</h1>
                    <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-xl text-left p-2 font-semibold">Eligibility Check Of Donor by Doctor</h1>
                </div>                
                <div class="step1 flex items-center gap-2 lg:mb-0 mb-4">
                    <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-xl bg-blue-600 text-white lg:w-16 lg:h-14 w-12 h-12 rounded-full text-center flex items-center justify-center font-semibold">3</h1>
                    <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-xl text-left p-2 font-semibold">Eligibility Check Of Donor by Doctor</h1>
                </div>                
                <div class="step1 flex items-center gap-2 lg:mb-0 mb-4">
                    <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-xl bg-red-600 text-white lg:w-16 lg:h-14 w-12 h-12 rounded-full text-center flex items-center justify-center font-semibold">4</h1>
                    <h1 class="lg:text-2xl text-xl text-left p-2 font-semibold">Eligibility Check Of Donor by Doctor</h1>
                </div>                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 flex">
        <div class="bg-gray-200 py-8 lg:px-14 px-4 lg:py-16 w-full items-left justify-center flex flex-col">
            <p class="mb-1 text-lg font-bold text-red-700 lg:text-xl dark:text-red-400">Guidline</p>
            <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none text-gray-900 md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl dark:text-white">Guidline for RedHop Donation</h1>   
            <div class=" lg:mt-2">
                <ul class="max-w-md space-y-4 text-gray-500 list-inside dark:text-gray-400">
                    <li class="flex font-bold">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 me-2 mt-[2px] text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        A person having age betweeen 18 to 60 years, can donate RedHope
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex font-bold">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 me-2 mt-[2px] text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        A Woman who got pregnant once can't no donate RedHope
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex font-bold">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 me-2 mt-[2px] text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        If Vaccinated, Person can donate after 28 Days of 1st Dose of Vaccination
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex font-bold">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 me-2 mt-[2px] text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Donors can donate RedHope in every 15 days, but till 4 months from being tested positive.
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex font-bold">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 me-2 mt-[2px] text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        A person having suger or hypertension but in control from last 1 month without changing any medicine can donate RedHope
                    </li>
                </ul>     
            </div>
        </div>
        <img src={donor2.src} alt="" class="lg:block hidden w-full h-full object-cover">
    </div>
</section>
